column3: Good news, adventurer! While you were away, Mistress Krile completed her work on the Aethernet relay, allowing us to access another region of the island!
I'm told it's quite different from Anemos─far, far colder, on account of a preponderance of ice-aspected aether. Accordingly, the team dubbed it “Pagos.”
They've already established a new base camp, and if you'd like to lend a hand with the expedition, you'd be more than welcome.
Just say the word and I'll see to the arrangements. I'm sure Mistress Krile will be overjoyed to see you again!
You now have access to the Forbidden Land, Eureka Pagos. Like Anemos, Pagos can be explored in parties of up to eight players, or solo.
To embark on your journey to Pagos, speak with Rodney at Pier #1 in Kugane.

Please be advised that all excursions into the Forbidden Land, Eureka Pagos, are item level synced. Gear exceeding an item level of <Sheet(ContentFinderCondition,IntegerParameter(1),18)/> will be adjusted.
